data.value: The end result depends on the item selected in the Scores tab, under the Score table. If the value is Crisp, the end result will show Fuzzy numbers (or single numbers if the user chooses to display Crisp Value) If the value is Fuzzy, the end result will show intervals. If the calculations shows incorrect values, try changing the value in the combo list described above.
